            <title><![CDATA[多倫多民運會六四紀念碑獻花　嘆維園燭光為中國民主燈塔　港移民必為自由同抗爭]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<figure class="image"><picture><source srcset="/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2021/05/六四32-20210531192403_28ab_large.jpg" media="(min-width: 960px)"><source srcset="/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2021/05/六四32-20210531192403_28ab_medium.jpg" media="(min-width: 720px)"><source srcset="/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2021/05/六四32-20210531192403_28ab_small.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2021/05/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B32-20210531192403_28ab_large.jpg" alt referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture>
